text: Thierry Poyet (born March 25, 1965) is a Monegasque politician. He was elected to the National Council in the 2013 Monegasque election as a member for the ruling coalition, Horizon Monaco. ==External links== * Biography on the National Council website * Thierry Poyet on Twitter Category:Living people Category:1965 births Category:Monegasque politicians
